sec.p:
Next, we discuss the effects of various point defects on the electronic, optical and thermoelectric characteristics of 1L 1T′ WTe2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
